::Prowl::

The doors to the CR room open, Prowl walking in, one arm around Iron Raptor. 
He walks to a CR chamber, looking back at Iron Raptor. After she was 
repaired, he could give her a tour of the ship, make her at home in their new 
base. He leans toward her, kissing her on the lips as his other arm encircles 
her, holding her in his embrace. He leans back, looking at the face of his 
love.

"Allright, get yourself repaired," he says, smiling at her.
